quran[246]{c,v,t}:
  41,47,"Luqondene naye ulwazi lwehora futhi asikho isithelo esiphumayo ekhasini laso futhi akekho owesifazane okhulelwayo noma azale ngaphandle kolwazi lwakhe futhi ngosuku lapho ebabiza (ethi) “baphi abahlanganyeli bami bayothi, “ siyamemezela kuwena ukuthi akekho phakathi kwethu ufakazi”"
  41,48,Futhi kuyonyamalala kubona lokho ababekubiza ngaphambilini futhi bayocabanga ukuthi abanayo indawo yokukhosela
  41,49,Umuntu akakhathali ukucela okuhle kepha uma ethintwa okubi uphatheka kabi aphelelwe yithemba
  41,50,"Futhi uma simzwisa umusa ovela kuthina emva kokuba ukuhlupheka sekumthintile ngempela uthi, “lokhu kungokwami futhi angicabangi ukuthi ihora liyofika futhi uma ngiphindiselwe"
  41,51,"eNkosini yami ngempela okwami okuhle kakhulu kuyona, ngakho-ke ngempela siyobatshela labo abangakholwanga ngalokho ababekwenza futhi ngempela siyobazwisa isijeziso esinzima"
  41,52,Futhi uma sikhombisa umusa kumuntu uyahoxa futhi afulathele kepha uma ethintwa okubi wenza umthandazo omude
  41,53,"Ithi, “ngakube nibonile yini uma ivela kuMvelinqangi (iQur’an) nabeseniyayiphika, ngakube ngubani oduke kakhulu kunalowo osekuhlubukeni okukude le!”"
  41,54,"Siyobakhombisa izimpawu zethu emhlabeni kanye nasemiphefumulweni yabo kuze kube sobala kubona ukuthi yona iyiqiniso, ngakube akwanele yini ukuthi iNkosi yakho yona ingufakazi phezulu kwezinto zonke? 55. Bheka! Ngempela bona basekungabazeni mayelana nokuhlangana ne Nkosi yabo, Bheka! Ngempela yona ingamele zonke izinto"
  42,1,Ha Meem
  42,2,Ain Sin Qaf
  42,3,"Kanjalo uyakwembula kuwena kanye nakulaba ababengaphambilini kwakho, nguMvelinqangi ophakeme ngamandla onobuhlakani"
  42,4,"Kungokwakhe noma ngabe yini esemazulwini kanye noma ngabe yini esemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme kakhulu, mkhulu"
  42,5,Amazulu angase adabuke phakathi ngaphezulu kwawo futhi izingelosi zigubha indumiso yeNkosi yazo futhi zicelela labo abasemhlabeni intethelelo bheka! Ngempela uMvelinqangi yena ungothethelelayo onesihawu
  42,6,"Futhi labo abathatha (abanye) abavikeli esikhundleni sakhe, uMvelinqangi ungumlondolozi phezulu kwabo futhi wena awusiyena umphathi phezulu kwabo"
  42,7,"Futhi kanjalo siyembulile kuwena iQur’an ngesi-Arabhu ukuze uxwayise unina wamadolobha kanye noma ngabe ngobani abawazungelezile futhi uxwayise ngosuku lokuhlangana, akukho ukungabaza ngalo, ingxenye iyokuba sesivandeni futhi (enye) ingxenye ibe semlilweni ovuthayo"
  42,8,Futhi ukube uMvelinqangi wayethanda wayezobenza isizwe esisodwa kepha ufaka lowo amthandayo emseni wakhe futhi izoni azinaye umvikeli noma umsizi
  42,9,"Noma ngakube bazithathela abavikeli esikhundleni sakhe, kepha nguMvelinqangi ongumvikeli futhi yena uphilisa abafile futhi yena wenza zonke izinto"
  42,10,"Futhi noma ngabe yini eniphikisana kuyona, ngakho-ke isehlulelo sayo sikuMvelinqangi, lowo nguMvelinqangi iNkosi yami ngethembele kuyena futhi ngiphendukela kuyona ngokuzisola"
  42,11,"Umdali wamazulu nomhlaba wanenzela phakathi kwenu ngakubili futhi nasezinkomeni ngakubili, uyaniphindaphinda akukho lutho olufana naye futhi yena ungozwayo obonayo"
  42,12,"Ngezakhe izihluthulelo zamazulu nomhlaba. Uyaselula isabelo kunoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo futhi anciphise, ngempela yena uyisazi sazo zonke izinto"
  42,13,"UMvelinqangi wanibekela inkolo leyo ayibekela uNowa kanye naleyo esiyembulile kuwena kanye nesayembula ku- Abrahamu nakuMose kanye nakuJesu ukuthi baqinise inkolo, futhi ningaqembukelani kuyona, kunzima kulabo abakhonza izithombe lokho enibamemela kukona, uMvelinqangi uziqokela lowo amthandayo futhi uholela kuyena lowo ophendukela kuyena ngokuzisola"
  42,14,"Futhi babengaqembukelene kwaze kwaba yingaphambili kokuba sebefikelwe ulwazi ngenxa yomona nenzondo phakathi kwabo futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yegama eselidlulile elivela eNkosini yakho esikhathini esimisiwe kwakuzokwehlulelwa phakathi kwabo, futhi ngempela labo ababenziwe ukuthi badle ifa lencwadi emva kwabo ngempela basekungabazeni okunzima ngayo"
  42,15,"Ngakho-ke kulokho mema futhi ume uqine njengokuba uphoqiwe futhi ungalandeli izifiso zabo futhi ithi, “ngikholiwe kulokho okwembulwa nguMvelinqangi okuyincwadi futhi ngiphoqiwe ukuthi ngenze ubulungiswa phakathi kwenu, uMvelinqangi yiNkosi yethu neNkosi yenu, okwethu yimisebenzi yethu nokwenu yimisebenzi yenu, ayikho impikiswanophakathikwethunani, uMvelinqangiuyosiqoqela ndawonye futhi kukuyena ukuphindela kokugcina"
  42,16,Futhi labo abaphikisanayo ngoMvelinqangi emva kokuba sekwamukeliwe impikiswano yabo iyize leze eNkosini yabo futhi phezulu kwabo kunentukuthelo (kaMvelinqangi) futhi okwabo yisijeziso esinzima
  42,17,"NguMvelinqangi owembula incwadi ngeqiniso nangesikalo, futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi mhlawumbe ihora selisondele"
  42,18,Ukulisheshisa (ihora bayakufisa) labo abangakholelwa kulona kulapho labo abakholwayo belesaba futhi bayazi ukuthi lona liyiqiniso bheka! Ngempela labo abaphikisanayo mayelana nehora ngempela basekudukeni okukude le
  42,19,"UMvelinqangi unomusa ezincekwini zakhe wabela noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo futhi yena uqatha, ungophakeme ngamandla"
  42,20,Noma ngabe ngubani ofisa isivuno sempilo ezayo siyamunezelela esivunweni sakhe futhi noma ngabe ngubani ofisa isivuno salomhlaba simunika sona futhi empilweni ezayo angeke abenayo ingxenye
  42,21,"Noma ngakube banabahlanganyeli ababamisele inkolo, lokho angakuvumelanga uMvelinqangi futhi ukube kwakungesingenxa yegama lamanqamu ngempela kwakuzokwehlulelwa phakathi kwabo futhi ngempela izoni okwazo yisijeziso esibuhlungu"
  42,22,"Uyozibona izoni zesaba ngenxa yezakusebenzela futhi kona kwehlela kubona futhi labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okulungileyo bayokuba sezimfundeni zezivande, okwabo kuyoba yinoma ngabe yini abayifunayo ngaphambili kweNkosi yabo, lowo ngumusa omkhulu"
  42,23,"Lokho, yilokho uMvelinqangi akutshela izinceku zakhe njengezindaba ezinhle lezo ezakholwa futhi ezenza okulungileyo, ithi, “angiwuceli umvuzo kunina ngakho ngaphandle kothando ezihlotsheni zami nakunoma ngabe ngubani osebenzela okuhle siyomunezelela kukona okuhle, ngempela uMvelinqangi ungothethelelayo obongayo"
  42,24,"Noma bathi, “uqambela uMvelinqangi amanga ngakho-ke uma uMvelinqangi ethanda uyayisicilela inhliziyo yakho, futhi uMvelinqangi uyawasusa amanga aqinisekise iqiniso ngamazwi akhe, ngempela yena uyisazi salokho okusezifubeni"
  42,25,Futhi nguyena owamukela ukuphenduka ezincekwini zakhe futhi othethelela izenzo ezimbi futhi (uMvelinqangi) uyakwazi lokho enikwenzayo
  42,26,"Futhi uyabaphendula labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo futhi abanezelele emseni wakhe, futhi abangakholwa okwabo yisijeziso esinzima"
  42,27,"Futhi ukube uMvelinqangi wayeselulile isabelo sezinceku zakhe ngempela zazizohlubuka emhlabeni, kepha usehlisa ngendlela athanda ngayo ngempela yena ngezinceku zakhe uyazi uyabona"
  42,28,Futhi nguyena owehlisela phansi imvula emuva kokuba bephelelwe yithemba futhi awusabalalise umusa wakhe futhi yena ungumvikeli ofanele ukudunyiswa
  42,29,Futhi ezinye zezimpawu zakhe yindalo yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke akusakaza kukona kokubili (amazulu nomhlaba) okuyizidalwa ezinyakazayo futhi yena unawo amandla okubaqoqela ndawonye uma ethanda
  42,30,Futhi noma ngabe yiliphi ishwa elinivelelayo kungenxa yalokho izandla zenu ezikusebenzele futhi (uMvelinqangi) uyathethelela kakhulu
  42,31,Futhi nina aniyibona abaphunyukayo emhlabeni futhi aninaye umvikeli nomelekeleli ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi
  42,32,"Futhi ezimpawini zakhe imikhumbi olwandle, okusengathi yizintaba"
  42,33,"Uma ethanda uyawuthulisa umoya, bese (ulwandle) lunganyakazi endaweni yalo yangaphezulu, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kulowo nalowo obekezelayo, obongayo"
  42,34,"Noma ababhubhise ngenxa yalokho abakusebenzela, futhi uyathethelela kakhulu"
  42,35,Futhi bayazi labo abaphikisanayo ngamavesi ethu (ukuthi) abanayo indawo yokuphephela
  42,36,Ngakho-ke noma ngabe yini eninikwe yona yinjabulo yempilo yalomhlaba futhi lokho okukuMvelinqangi kungcono futhi kuyahlala kulabo abakholwayo futhi abathembela eNkosini yabo
  42,37,Kanye nalabo abagwema izono ezinkulu nokukhohlakala futhi okuthi uma bethukuthele bathethelele
  42,38,Nalabo abaphendulayo eNkosini yabo futhi abenza umthandazo futhi abenza udaba lwabo (lunqunywe) yisigungu phakathi kwabo futhi abasebenzisa kulokho esababela kona
  42,39,Nalabo okuthi uma behlelwa yingcindezelo baziphindiselele
  42,40,"Futhi umvuzo wokubi okubi okufana nako, ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani othethelelayo futhi alungise umvuzo wakhe ukuMvelinqangi, ngempela yena akazithandi izoni"
  42,41,Futhi ngempela noma ngabe ngubani oziphindiselayo emva kokuba ecindezelwe ngakho-ke labo abanayo indlela (yokusolwa)
  42,42,"Kuphela indlela (yokusolwa) ikulabo abenza okungenabo ubulungiswa kubantu, futhi abacindezelayo emhlabeni ngokungesilona iqiniso, labo-ke okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu"
  42,43,Futhi ngempela noma ngabe ngubani obekezelayo futhi athethelele ngempela lokho kuwukulungisa izindaba
  42,44,"Futhi lowo oshiywa nguMvelinqangi ekudukeni, ngakho-ke akanaye umvikeli emva kwakhe futhi uyobona izoni okuyothi uma sezibona isijeziso zithi, “ngakube ikhona yini indlela yokuphindela?”"
  42,45,"Futhi uyobona belethwa ngaphambili kwaso bethotshiswe yinjabhiso bebheka ngokujeqeza okufifiyelayo, futhi labo abakholwayo bayothi, “ngempela abalahlekelwe yilabo abalahlekelwa yimiphefumulo yabo kanye nemindeni yabo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo, bheka ngempela izoni zisesijezisweni esingapheliyo.”"
  42,46,Futhi angeke babenabo abavikeli abayobalekelela ngaphandle kukaMvelinqangi futhi noma ngabe ngubani uMvelinqangi amshiya ekudukeni akanayo indlela
  42,47,"Phendulani iNkosi yenu ngaphambi kokuba kufike usuku olungeke lugwenywe oluvela kuMvelinqangi, angeke nibe nesiphephelo ngalolosuku futhi angeke niphike"
  42,48,"Kepha uma befulathela, ngakho-ke asikuthumelanga kubona njengomlondolozi, awukho (umthwalo) ophezulu kwakho ngaphandle kokudlulisela (umyalezo) futhi ngempela uma sizwisa umuntu umusa ovela kuthina uyawuthokozela futhi uma behlelwa okubi ngenxa yalokho izandla zabo ezikulethe ngaphambili, ngakho-ke umuntu akabongi"
  42,49,"UngokaMvelinqangi umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba, udala noma ngabe yini ayithandayo, unikeza lowo amthandayo (ingane) yesifazane futhi unikeza lowo amthandayo (ingane) yesilisa"
  42,50,Noma abanike kokubili isilisa nesifazane futhi wenza inyumba noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo ngempela yena ungowaziyo owenza (izinto zonke)
  42,51,"Futhi akusikona okomuntu ukuthi uMvelinqangi akhulume naye ngaphandle kwesambulo noma ngemumva kwesembozo noma athumele isithunywa ukuze sembule ngentando yakhe noma ngabe yini ayithandayo, ngempela yena uphakeme unobuhlakani"
  42,52,"Futhi kanjalo sasembula kuwena isambulo ngempoqo yethu, wawungazi ukuthi yini incwadi noma inkolo, kepha sayenza yaba ukukhanya esihola ngako noma ngabe ngubani esimthandayo ezincekwini zethu futhi ngempela wena uholela endleleni eqondile"
  42,53,"Indlela kaMvelinqangi okunguyena okungokwakhe konke okusemazulwini nakho konke okusemhlabeni, ngempela ikuMvelinqangi lapho izindaba ziyoya khona ekugcineni"
  43,1,Ha Meem
  43,2,Ngencwadi ecacile
  43,3,Ngempela siyenze yaba iQur’an engesi-Arabhu ukuze niqonde
  43,4,Futhi ngempela yona ikumama wencwadi okuthina ophakeme onobuhlakani
  43,5,Ngakube sizosusa isikhumbuzo kunina ngoba ningabantu abamoshayo
  43,6,Futhi bangaki abaphrofethi esabathumela emandulo
  43,7,Futhi kwakungakaze kufike kubona umphrofethi ngaphandle kokuthi babemenza inhlekisa
  43,8,Ngakho-ke sababhubhisa labo ababeqatha kunabo ngamandla futhi sesadlula isibonelo sabasendulo
  43,9,"Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owadala amazulu nomhlaba ngempela bangathi, “owawadala ophakeme ngamandla owaziyo”"
  43,10,Okunguyena owanenzela umhlaba waba yindawo yokuphumula futhi wanenzela kuwona izindlela ukuze niholeke
  43,11,"Futhi okunguyena owehlisela phansi amanzi avela esibhakabhakeni ngesilinganiso wayesevusa ngawo izwe elifile, niyovuswa kanjalo"
  43,12,Futhi okunguyena owadala zonke izinto ngambili futhi wanenzela imikhumbi kanye nezinkomo lezo enizigibelayo
  43,13,"Ukuze nigibele emihlane yazo bese nikhumbula umusa weNkosi yenu uma senigibele phezulu kwazo bese nithi, “udumo malube kulowo osenzele lokhu futhi thina besingeke sibenako”"
  43,14,Futhi ngempela eNkosini yethu siyophindela
  43,15,"Futhi bambekela ingxenye ezincekwini zakhe, ngempela umuntu akabongi ngokucacile"
  43,16,Noma ngakube wazithathela kulokho akudalayo amadodakazi wayesenikhethela amadodana na
  43,17,"Futhi uma oyedwa wabo etshelwa ngezindaba zalokho akwenzile okuyisibonelo konomusa, ubuso bakhe bubamnyama futhi agcwale usizi"
  43,18,Lowo okhuliswe ngemihlobiso kulapho yena esempikiswaneni engacacile
  43,19,"Futhi benza izingelosi isifazane lezo okuyizona eziyizinceku zonomusa, ngakube bakubona ukudalwa kwazo na"
  43,20,"Futhi bathi, “ukube wayethanda onomusa sasingeke sibakhonze”, abanalo ulwazi lwaloko (abenzi) lutho ngaphandle kokuqamba amanga"
  43,21,Noma sabanikeza incwadi ngaphambilini kwayo bona ababambelele kuyona
  43,22,"Kepha bathi, “ngempela thina safumana obaba bethu besendleleni futhi ngempela thina siholeleka ezinyathelweni zabo”"
  43,23,"Futhi kanjalo asizange ngaphambilini kwakho sithumele edolobheni (ebantwini) umxwayisi ngaphandle kokuthi abanothile balo bathi, “ngempela thina safumana obaba bethu besendleleni futhi ngempela nathi silandela ezinyathelweni zabo”"
  43,24,"Wathi “yize noma nginilethele ukuholwa okungcono kunalokho enabafumana kukona obaba benu? Bathi, “ngempela thina asikholelwa kulokho othunywe nako”"
  43,25,"Ngakho-ke saziphindisela kubona, bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho sabaphikayo"
  43,26,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi u-Abrahamu ethi kuyise nakubantu bakubo, “Angihlangene nalokho enikukhonzayo"
  43,27,Ngaphandle kwalowo owangidala futhi ngempela uzongihola
  43,28,Futhi wakwenza kwaba yigama eliseleyo ezizukulwaneni ukuze ziphenduke
  43,29,"Kepha, ngabanika injabulo laba kanye naboyise kwaze kwaba yilapho befikelwa yiqiniso kanye nesithunywa esicacile"
  43,30,"Futhi kwathi lapho sebefikelwa yiqiniso bathi, “leli yilumbo futhi ngempela thina asikholelwa kulona”"
  43,31,"Futhi bathi, “kungani ingembulwanga leQur’an emadodeni amakhulu amadolobha amakhulu"
  43,32,"Ngakube bona bayawuhlukanisa umusa weNkosi yakho, yithina esehlukanisayo phakathi kwabo ekuphileni kwabo empilweni yakulomhlaba futhi sabaphakamisa abanye babo ngaphezulu kwabanye ngamazinga ukuze abanye babo basebenzele abanye futhi umusa weNkosi yakho ungcono kunalokho abakuqoqela ndawonye"
  43,33,"Futhi ukube abantu babengesisona isizwe esisodwa, ngempela sasizobenzela labo abangakholwa konomusa uphahla lwesiliva ezindlini zabo kanye nezitebhisi abanyuka ngazo"
  43,34,Futhi okwezindlu zabo yiminyango kanye nemibhede abaphumula phezulu kwayo
  43,35,"Nomhlobiso wegolide, futhi konke lokho kuyinjabulo yempilo yalomhlaba futhi impilo ezayo eNkosini yakho ngeyabagwema okubi"
  43,36,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ofulathela isikhumbuzo sonomusa simvulela usathane ukuthi abe ngumngane wakhe
  43,37,Futhi ngempela bona (osathane) bayabavimbela endleleni futhi bacabanga ukuthi bona bangabaholiwe
  43,38,"Kuze kube yilapho efika kuthina athi, “ukube nje phakathi kwami nawe bekunebanga lezimpumalanga ezimbili, ububi umngane omubi"
  43,39,Futhi angeke kunisize namhlanje njengoba nenza okungenabo ubulungiswa ukuthi nina niyahlukaniselana esijezisweni
  43,40,Ngakube wena ungazenza yini izithuli ukuthi zizwe noma uhole izimpumputhe kanye noma ngabe ngubani osekudukeni okucacile
  43,41,"Noma ngabe siyakuthatha, ngempela thina siyoziphindisela kubona"
  43,42,"Noma sikukhombise lokho esabakhombisa kona, ngakho-ke ngempela sinamandla phezulu kwabo"
  43,43,"Ngakho-ke bambelela kulokho okwambuliwe kuwena, ngempela wena usendleleni eqondile"
  43,44,Futhi ngempela yona iyisikhumbuzo kuwena nakubantu bakho futhi niyobuzwa
  43,45,"Futhi buza noma ngabe ngobani esabathumela ngaphambilini kwakho abayizithunywa zethu, ngakube ngaphandle konomusa sibenzele yini izithixo ukuba bazikhonze"
  43,46,"Futhi ngempela samuthumela uMose namavesi ethu kuFaro kanye nakubabusi bakhe, ngakho-ke wathi, “ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa seNkosi yemihlaba”"
  43,47,Kepha kwathi lapho esefika kubona nezimpawu zethu kwaba yilapho bezihleka
  43,48,"Futhi asizange sibakhombise uphawu ngaphandle kokuba lubelukhulu kunolukanye nalo, futhi sabathatha ngesijeziso ukuze mhlawumbe babuye"
  43,49,"Futhi bathi, “Oh mlumbi! Sibizele iNkosi yakho ngalokho eyenza isethembiso ngako nawe, ngempela thina sizokuba ngabaholiwe”"
  43,50,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sesisisusile kubona isijeziso kwaba yilapho bona besephula (isethembiso)
  43,51,"Futhi uFaro wamemeza phakathi kwabantu bakhe wathi “O Bantu bami! Abusibona yini na obami ubukhosi base- Gibhithe? Kanye nalemifula egeleza ngaphansi kwami, ngakube aniboni yini"
  43,52,Ngakube angingcono yini kunalowo odelelekile (uMose) futhi akakwazi ukukhuluma ngokucacile
  43,53,Ngakho-ke kungani engabekwanga phezulu kwakhe amasongo egolide noma izingelosi zize kanye naye
  43,54,"Ngakho-ke uFaro wabakhohlisa abantu bakhe base beyamhlonipha, ngempela bona babengabantu abephula umthetho"
  43,55,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho besithukuthelisa saziphindisela kubona sabaminzisa bonke
  43,56,Futhi sabenza asebedlulile kanye nesibonelo kwabeza ngemumva
  43,57,FuthikwathilaphoindodanakaMariyayenziwanjengesibonelo kwaba yilapho abantu bakho bebanga umsindo ngayo (ngayo)
  43,58,"Futhi bathi, “ngakube onkulunkulu bethu abangcono noma uyena” abakwenzi lokho njengesibonelo ngaphandle kwempikiswano, kepha bona bangabantu abathanda ukuxabana"
  43,59,Akayilutho ngaphandle kokuba yinceku esabeka umusa phezulu kwayo futhi samenza wabayisibonelo ebantwini bakwa-Israyeli
  43,60,Futhi ukube sasithanda sasizokwenza izingelosi phakathi kwenu emhlabeni zibe ngezilandelayo
  43,61,"Futhi ngempela yena uwuphawu lwehora ngakho-ke ungangabazi ngalo futhi landelani mina, lena yindlela eqondile"
  43,62,"Futhi usathane anganivimbeli, ngempela yena uyisitha senu esigqamile"
  43,63,"Futhi khumbula ngenkathi uJesu efika namavesi acacile wathi, “ngize kunina nobuhlakani nokuthi nginicacisele okunye kwalokho eniphikisana kukona ngakho-ke yesabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningihloniphe"
  43,64,"Ngempela uMvelinqangi yena uyiNkosi yami neNkosi yenu ngakho-ke mkhonzeni, lena yindlela eqondile"
  43,65,"Kepha amaqembu phakathi kwabo ayephikisana, Oh usizi! Kulabo ababenza okungenabo ubulungiswa, esijezisweni sosuku lokugcina"
  43,66,Ngakube balindele ngaphandle kwehora ukuthi lifike kubona masinyane kulapho bona bengaboni
  43,67,Abangane ngalolosuku abanye babo bayokuba yizitha zabanye ngaphandle kwabagwema ukubi
  43,68,Oh zinceku zami! Alukho uvalo kunina namhlanje futhi nina angeke nibe wusizi
  43,69,Labo abakholwayo emavesini ethu futhi abazithoba ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi
  43,70,Ngenani esivandeni nina namakhosikazi enu nithokoze
  43,71,Kuzungeleziswe kubona izingqoko (amathileyi) egolide nezinkomishi futhi phakathi kuzona kunalokho okufiswa yimiphefumulo nokuthokozisa amehlo futhi nina lapho phakathi niyohlala ingunaphakade
  43,72,Lesi yisivande enenziwe ukuthi nisidle njengefa ngenxa yalokho enanikwenza
  43,73,Okwethu lapho phakathi yizithelo eziningi enidla kuzona
  43,74,Ngempela izoni zisesijezisweni sesihogo ingunaphakade
  43,75,Angeke bancishiselwe sona (isijeziso) futhi bona lapho phakathi bayophelelwa yithemba
  43,76,"Futhi asizange senze okungenabo ubulungiswa kubona kepha, bona babengabenzi bokungenabo ubulungiswa"
  43,77,"Futhi bayokhala, “Oh malik! yenza ukuthi iNkosi yakho isiqedele (isibulale) lokhu uyothi (umalik) ngempela nina nizohlala (lapha)"
  43,78,Ngempela sinifikele neqiniso kepha iningi lenu liyalizonda iqiniso
  43,79,Noma ngakube balenzile yini icebo odabeni? Kepha yithina abenzi bamacebo
  43,80,"Noma bacabanga ukuthi asizizwa yini izimfihlo zabo nezingxoxo zabo zangasese, yebo! Futhi izithunywa zethu zikanye nabo ziyabhala"
  43,81,Ithi uma kungukuthi onomusa unendodana ngakho-ke ngingowokuqala wezikhonzi
  43,82,"Mayidunyiswe iNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba iNkosi yesihlalo sobukhosi, ngaphezulu kwalokho abakuchazayo"
  43,83,Ngakho-ke bayeke bakhulume futhi badlale kuze kube bayahlangana ngosuku lwabo lolo abathenjiswa lona
  43,84,Futhi yena uyilowo Mvelinqangi emazulwini futhi onguMvelinqangi emhlabeni futhi yena unobuhlakani uyisazi
  43,85,Futhi ugcwele izibusiso lowo okungowakhe umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili futhi lukuyena ulwazi lwehora futhi niyobuyiselwa kuyena
  43,86,Futhi labo abababizayo esikhundleni sakhe abanako ukuncengela ngaphandle kwalabo abafakazela iqiniso futhi bona bazi
  43,87,"Futhi uma ubabuza ukuthi ngubani owabadala, ngempela bazothi “nguMvelinqangi” baphendukiselwa kanjani emumva"
  43,88,"Futhi ukusho kwakhe, Oh Nkosi yami! Ngempela laba ngabantu abangakholwa"
  43,89,"Ngakho suka kubo futhi uthi, \"Ukuthula.\" Kepha bazokwazi"
  44,1,Ha Meem
  44,2,Ngencwadi ecacile
  44,3,"Ngempela\tsayithumela\tphansi\tebusuku\tobubusisiwe, ngempela thina sasingabaxwayisi"
  44,4,"Kubona\t(ubusuku)\tkunqunywe\tzonke\tizindaba ezonobuhlakani"
  44,5,"Udaba oluvela kuthina, ngempela thina sasingabathumeli"
  44,6,"Umusa ovela eNkosini yakho, ngempela yona ingezwayo eyaziyo"
  44,7,INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ukube nina beniqinisekile
  44,8,"Akukho okunokukhonzwa ngaphandle kwakhe (uMvelinqangi) uyaphilisa futhi uyabulala, iNkosi yenu neNkosi yobaba benu basendulo"
  44,9,"Kepha bona basekungabazeni, bayazidlalela nje"
  44,10,Ngakho-ke lindela usuku lapho isibhababhaka siyoletha intuthu egqamile
  44,11,"Imboza abantu, lesi yisijeziso esibuhlungu"
  44,12,"Nkosi\tyethu\tsisuse\tkuthina\tisijeziso,\tngempela singabakholwayo"
  44,13,Bangaba kanjani nesikhumbuzo kulapho sezafika kubona izithunywa ezicacile
  44,14,"Babe sebeyasifulathela (isithunywa) futhi bathi, “sifundisiwe futhi siyahlanya”"
  44,15,"Ngempela\tsiyasisusa\tisijeziso\tkancane\tngempela\tnina niyaphindela (ekoneni)"
  44,16,"Ngosuku lapho siyobashaya ngokushaya okukhulu, ngempela thina singabaziphindiselayo"
  44,17,"Futhi ngempela sabalinga ngaphambilini kwabo abantu baFaro, futhi safika kubona isithunywa esihloniphekile"
  44,18,"(UMose wathi), “zikhulule zize kimina izinceku zikaMvelinqangi, ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esihloniphekile kunina”"
  44,19,"Futhi ningaziphakamisi ngokuphambene noMvelinqangi, ngempela mina ngize kunina negunya elicacile"
  44,20,Futhi ngempela ngifune isiphephelo eNkosini yami neNkosi yenu hleze ningikhande ngamatshe
  44,21,"Kepha uma ningangikholwa, ngakho-ke qhelelanani nami"
  44,22,(UMose) wabe esebiza iNkosi yakhe ukuthi laba bangabantu abayizoni
  44,23,Ngakho-ke hamba nezinceku zami ebusuku ngempela nina nizolandelwa
  44,24,Futhi ushiye ulwandle lucwebile ngempela bona bayimpi ezominza
  44,25,Zingaki izivande nemithombo abayishiya ngemumva
  44,26,Kanye namasimu nezindawo ezinhle
  44,27,Nobuntofontofo (bempilo) ababethokoza kubona
  44,28,"Kanjalo\tsabenza\tabanye\tabantu\tbabayizindlalifa\tzawo (umhlaba)"
  44,29,Ngakho-ke izulu nomhlaba akuzange kubakhalele futhi abazange baphunyuzwe (abantu baFaro)
  44,30,"Futhi\tngempela\tsabasindisa\tabantwana\tbakwa-Israyeli esijezisweni esidumazayo"
  44,31,"KuFaro, ngempela yena wayephakeme phakathi kwabakhonza izithombe"
  44,32,Futhi ngempela sabakhetha ngolwazi ngaphezulu kwemihlaba
  44,33,Futhi sabanika ezimpawini okunokulingwa okucacile kuzona
  44,34,Ngempela laba bathi
  44,35,Akuyilutho lokho ngaphandle kokufa kwethu kokuqala futhi thina angeke sivuswe kwabafileyo
  44,36,Ngakho-ke lethani obaba bethu uma kungukuthi nina ningabaqinisileyo
  44,37,Ngakube bona bangcono noma abantu baseTubba kanye nalabo ababengaphambilini kwabo na? Sababhubhisa ngempela bona babeyizoni
  44,38,Futhi asizange siwadale amazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngokudlala
  44,39,Asizange sikudale kokubili (amazulu nomhlaba) ngaphandle kweqiniso kepha iningi labo alazi
  44,40,Ngempela usuku lokwahlulela yisikhathi esinqunyelwe bona bonke
  44,41,Usuku lapho umngane engeke amsize ngalutho umngane futhi bona angeke balekelelwe
  44,42,"Ngaphandle\tkwalabo\tuMvelinqangi\tanomusa\tkubona, ngempela yena ungophakeme ngamandla onesihawu"
  44,43,Ngempela isihlahla sezaqum
  44,44,Ukudla kwezoni
  44,45,"Njengamafutha abilayo, abila eziswini"
  44,46,Njengokugxabha kwamanzi abilayo
  44,47,Mthatheni bese nimdonsela maphakathi nesihogo
  44,48,Bese nithela phezulu kwekhanda lakhe isijeziso samanzi abilayo
  44,49,"Yizwa,\tngempela\twena\twawuphakeme\tngamandla uhloniphekile"
  44,50,Ngempela lokhu yilokho nina enanikungabaza
  44,51,Ngempela abalungileyo bayokuba sendaweni ephephile
  44,52,Ezivandeni nasemithonjeni
  44,53,Begqoke usilika nokuhlotshiswe ngokugqamile bebhekene
  44,54,Kanjalo siyobashadisa namakhosikazi amahle anamehlo amahle amakhulu
  44,55,"Lapho\tphakathi\tbayobiza\tzonke\t(izinhlobo)\tzezithelo ngokuthula bephephile"
  44,56,Lapho phakathi angeke bakuzwe ukufa ngaphandle kokufa kokuqala futhi uyobasindisa esijezisweni somlilo ovuthayo
  44,57,"Ngumusa ovela eNkosini yakho, lokho ukuphumelela okukhulu"
  44,58,"Ngempela\tsakwenza\tkwabalula\tolimini\tlwakho\tukuze bakhumbule"
  44,59,Ngakho-ke linda ngempela bona bangabalindileyo
  45,1,Ha Meem
  45,2,"Isambulo\rsencwadi\rsivela\rkuMvelinqangi\rophakeme\rngamandla onobuhlakani"
  45,3,Ngempela emazulwini nasemhlabeni kunezimpawu kwabakholwayo
  45,4,Futhi ekudalweni kwenu nakho konke nakusakazayo (emhlabeni) okuyizidalwa ezinyakazayo kuyizimpawu kubantu abaqinisekile (enkolweni)
  45,5,Futhi ukuphambana kobusuku nemini kanye nalokho okwehliselwaphansinguMvelinqangiokuvelaesibhakabhakeni okuyisabelo (imvula) bese ephilisa ngayo umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo nokushintsha kwemimoya kuyizimpawu kubantu abanomqondo
  45,6,Lawa ngamavesi kaMvelinqangi siwafundela wena ngeqiniso ngakho-ke iyiphi inkulumo abayokholwa yiyo emva kukaMvelinqangi nezimpawu namavesi akhe
  45,7,Usizi kulowo nalowo mqambimanga oyisoni
  45,8,"Owezwayo amavesi kaMvelinqangi efundelwa wona bese eqhubeka nokuziqhenya, kube sengathi akawezwa, ngakho-ke mtshene ngesijeziso esibuhlungu"
  45,9,Futhi uma esekufundile okuthize emavesini ethu ukuthatha njengenhlekisa labo-ke okwabo yisijeziso esijabhisayo
  45,10,Ngaphambili kwabo kunesihogo futhi angeke kubasize ngalutho lokho ababekusebenzela ngisho nalokho abakuthatha njengabavikeli esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi futhi okwabo yisijeziso esikhulu
  45,11,"Lokhu ukuholwa, futhi labo abangakholelwa emavesini eNkosi yabo okwabo yisijeziso esibuhlungu seRijz"
  45,12,NguMvelinqangi owanenzela ulwandle lwanithobela ukuze imikhumbi ihambe kulona ngempoqo yakhe futhi ukuze nifune ububele bakhe futhi ukuze nibonge
  45,13,"Futhi wanenzela yanithobela noma ngabe yini esemazulwini kanye nakho konke okusemhlabeni, kuvela kuyena, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kubantu abacabangayo"
  45,14,Ithi kulabo abakholwayo abathethelele labo abangazethembi izinsuku zikaMvelinqangi ukuze anike umvuzo abantu ngenxa yalokho ababekusebenzela
  45,15,Noma ngabe ngubani owenza izenzo ezinhle kungokwakhe uqobo futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza okubi ngakho-ke kuphambene naye bese nibuyiselwa eNkosini yenu
  45,16,Futhi ngempela sabanikeza abantwana bakwa-Israyeli incwadi nesehlulelo nobuphrofethi futhi sababela ezintweni ezinhle futhi sabakhetha ngaphezulu kwemihlaba
  45,17,"Futhi sabanikeza ubufakazi obucacile odabeni, ngakho-ke abazange baphikisane kwaze kwaba yingemumva kokuba sebefikelwe ulwazi ngenxa yomona phakathi kwabo, ngempela iNkosi yakho iyokwehlulela phakathi kwabo ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo kulokho ababephikisana kukona"
  45,18,"Sabe sesikwenza ukuthi ube sendleleni esemthethweni empoqweni, ngakho-ke yilandele, ungalandeli izifiso zalabo abangazi"
  45,19,"Ngempela bona abasoze bakusize ngalutho maqondana noMvelinqangi futhi ngempela izoni ezinye zazo zingabangane zezinye, kepha uMvelinqangi ungumvikeli wabalungileyo"
  45,20,Lokhu kuwukubona okucacile kubantu nokuholeleka (endleleni elungileyo) kanye nomusa kubantu abaqinisekile (enkolweni)
  45,21,"Noma ngakube labo abenza izenzo ezimbi bacabanga ukuthi siyobenza njengalabo abakholwayo futhi abenze okuhle okulungileyo? Iyalingana impilo yabo kanye nokufa kwabo, okubi yilokho abakwehlulelayo"
  45,22,"Futhi uMvelinqangi wadala amazulu nomhlaba ngeqiniso futhi ukuze anike umvuzo yonke imiphefumulo ngenxa yalokho eyakusebenzela, futhi bona angeke benziwe okungenabo ubulungiswa"
  45,23,"Ngakube umbonile yini lowo othathe njengonkulunkulu wakhe ukufisa kwakhe? Futhi uMvelinqangi umshiye ekudukeni ngenxa yolwazi futhi wasicilela ukuzwa kwakhe nenhliziyo yakhe futhi wabeka isembozo ekuboneni kwakhe, ngakho-ke ngubani ongamhola emva kukaMvelinqangi? Ngakube anikhumbuli yini na"
  45,24,"Futhi bathi, “akuyilutho ngaphandle kwempilo yethu yasemhlabeni, siyafa futhi siyaphila futhi akukho okungasibhubhisa ngaphandle kwesikhathi” futhi abanalo ulwazi ngalokho, kuphela bayazicabangela nje"
  45,25,"Futhi uma befundelwa amavesi ethu acacile, kuphela ukuphika kwabo ukuthi bathi, “lethani obaba bethu uma kungukuthi nina niqinisile”"
  45,26,"Yithi, “uMvelinqangi uyaniphilisa bese enenza ukuthi nife bese eniqoqela ndawonye ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo okungekho ukungabaza kulona, kepha iningi labantu alazi”"
  45,27,"Futhi ungokaMvelinqangi umbuso wamazulu nomhlaba futhi ngosuku lokufika kwehora, ngalolosuku bayolahlekelwa abalandeli bamanga"
  45,28,"Futhi uyozibona zonke izizwe ziguqe phansi, zonke izizwe ziyobizelwa kokubhalwe encwadini yazo, ngalolusuku nizonikwa umvuzo ngalokho enanikwenza"
  45,29,"Lena yincwadi yethu ekhuluma nani ngeqiniso, ngempela thina sasikubhala lokho enanikwenza"
  45,30,"Ngakho-ke labo abakholwayo futhi abenza okuhle okulungileyo iNkosi yabo iyobangenisa emseni wayo, lokho ukuphumelela okucacile"
  45,31,Kepha labo abangakholwanga ngakube akazange yini amavesi ami afundelwe nina? Nabe seniyazikhukhumeza futhi ningabantu abayizoni
  45,32,"Futhi uma kuthiwa ngempela isethembiso sikaMvelinqangi siyiqiniso nehora akukho ukungabaza kulona nathi “asazi ukuthi yini ihora, sicabanga umcabango nje futhi thina asenelisekile (ngalo)"
  45,33,Futhi buyovela kubona ububi baloko ababekwenza futhi kuyobazungeleza lokho ababenza ngako inhlekisa
  45,34,"Futhi kuyothiwa, “ngalolusuku sizonikhohlwa njengoba nakhohlwa ukuhlangana ngalolusuku lwenu”"
  45,35,Lokho kungenxa yokuthi nina nanithatha amavesi kaMvelinqangi njengenhlekisa futhi yanikhohlisa impilo yalomhlaba ngakho-ke ngalolusuku angeke bakhishwe kusona (isihogo) futhi bona angeke bemukelwe emseni kaMvelinqangi
  45,36,Ngakho-ke udumo ngolukaMvelinqangi iNkosi yamazulu neNkosi yezwe iNkosi yemihlaba
  45,37,Futhi ngobakhe ubukhosi emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla unobuhlakani